pokemon_list.description: The fire on the tip of its tail is a measure of its life. If healthy, its tail burns intensely.

pokemon_list.name: Ninetales
pokemon_list.description: Each of its nine tails is imbued with supernatural power, and it can live for a thousand years.

pokemon_list.name: Nidorina
pokemon_list.description: When it senses danger, it raises all the barbs on its body. These barbs grow slower than Nidorinos.

pokemon_list.name: Sandslash
pokemon_list.description: The spikes on its body are made up of its hardened hide. It rolls up and attacks foes with its spikes.

pokemon_list.name: Weedle
pokemon_list.description: It eats its weight in leaves every day. It fends off attackers with the needle on its head.

pokemon_list.name: Metapod
pokemon_list.description: A steel-hard shell protects its tender body. It quietly endures hardships while awaiting evolution.
